author: rhuijben
msg: Implement our standard way of commandline parsing in svnrdump and use this
to enable full interactive and non-interactive authorization handling.
(open_connection): Take common authorization options and use this to
setup the client context and authorization baton.
(SVNRDUMP_ERR): New macro, to fix error texts to not use "svn: "
(main): Use apr parser for parsing options. Convert characters where needed.
Cannonicalize url. Pass arguments to open_connection().
